data.description: Spacious home close to all that counts.  Large bedrooms and lots of living space. Step onto the covered front porch and proceed into the tiled entry flanked by study and dining/living area. Proceed to large, tiled kitchen open to spacious family room. Eat-in kitchen offers island with breakfast bar, pantry, desk/study area and abundant cabinet and counter space. Upper level offers large owners' retreat with in-suite bath boasting dual sink vanity, separate shower, garden tub, linen closet and walk-in closet. Generous sized secondary bedrooms, loft/game area and second bath round out the upper level. Other features include lower level half bath, large utility room, sprinkler system, fenced backyard and a super convenient area.
